#

Slow Cooker Apple Cranberry Sauce

250 min
$5
80 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 8

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

SauceSide Dish

Tags:

Slow CookerSauceThanksgiving

Description

A delightful blend of tart cranberries and sweet apples, perfect for holiday meals.

Ingredients

  • fresh cranberries: 12 ounces
  • apples (peeled and chopped): 2 cups
  • brown sugar: 1/2 cup
  • water: 1/2 cup
  • cinnamon: 1 teaspoon
  • nutmeg: 1/4 teaspoon
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
